name: LUNA refugee DAO
description:
Luna event will have a far-reaching impact on the development of cryptocurrency. At this moment, whether you have Luna or not, as long as you are a resident of the cryptoworld who has witnessed this event together, you should join this autonomous organization.

The project is of a public welfare nature. All the funds raised by the project will be used for the expenditure on the security review of project funds in the encryption industry. 100% of them will be managed and used by Dao. All holders of project tokens have the right to participate in decision-making, and the governance will be carried out in Aragon.
